{"tid":2323061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名香港男子上月飛往北京 在入境時為陰性 隔離14天後呈陽性  列由香港輸入的確診個案","createTime":"2020-12-13T00:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T00:58:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6cac36b4ca019810dc67ff2c411f4a70206c7bff","tid":2323061,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T00:44:57.000Z","msg":"北京出現一宗由香港輸入確診個案<br />\n<br />\n北京新增一宗由香港輸入的新型冠狀病毒確診個案。60歲男患者上月28日乘坐香港航空HX336航班到達北京，在海關進行核酸檢測，結果為陰性，但前日在集中隔離酒店觀察期滿前再進行核酸檢測，結果呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2370453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2370453&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=b0128e08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2370453</a>"},{"pid":"3e76bd8e85953755eb8c1758b9aeca55ded8ae07","tid":2323061,"uid":54728,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T00:45:47.000Z","msg":"兄地！香港不安全，別來！"},{"pid":"c4a6812b9fc9860ee8a1771d7651e3f803431a0f","tid":2323061,"uid":325118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T00:58:29.000Z","msg":"誅！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0261554a3d10652bc66ef811d4727e1afa42e5d","tid":2323061,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T00:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要係香港出境，唔理你係一個月後感染，定係弓年後感染，都當係香港輸入個案"}]}